<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 12:50:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>移植的未来：在排斥发生之前停止排斥 — Janine Gaiha-Rohrbach 博士 — Biogen</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-future-of-transplants-stopping-rejection-before-it-starts-dr-janine-gaiha-rohrbach-biogen</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 12:50:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-future-of-transplants-stopping-rejection-before-it-starts-dr-janine-gaiha-rohrbach-biogen</guid></item><item><title>科学家为下一代电子产品构建五合一“超级分子”</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-build-five-in-one-super-molecule-for-next-gen-electronics</link><description>混合合成策略使复杂的分子结构能够充当单个电子系统。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-build-five-in-one-super-molecule-for-next-gen-electronics.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 12:35:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-build-five-in-one-super-molecule-for-next-gen-electronics</guid></item><item><title>科学家称这种受欢迎的食物可以帮助你的身体清除微塑料</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-say-this-popular-food-could-help-your-body-get-rid-of-microplastics</link><description>研究人员发现，泡菜中的一种细菌可以结合并帮助将纳米塑料排出体外，这有望成为减少塑料积累的益生菌方法。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-say-this-popular-food-could-help-your-body-get-rid-of-microplastics2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 12:20:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-say-this-popular-food-could-help-your-body-get-rid-of-microplastics</guid></item><item><title>物理学家发现磁力机制，挑战 300 年前的摩擦定律</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/physicists-discover-magnetic-mechanism-that-challenges-a-300-year-old-law-of-friction</link><description>研究人员发现，在磁动力学驱动下，摩擦力可以在不接触的情况下发生，并且并不总是随着负载而增加。这种效应可以实现可控、无磨损的技术。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/physicists-discover-magnetic-mechanism-that-challenges-a-300-year-old-law-of-friction2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 12:05:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/physicists-discover-magnetic-mechanism-that-challenges-a-300-year-old-law-of-friction</guid></item><item><title>美国宇航局刚刚在小行星贝努样本中发现了一些奇怪的东西</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/nasa-just-found-something-strange-inside-asteroid-bennu-sample</link><description>研究小行星贝努样本的科学家在最微小的尺度上发现了令人惊讶的复杂化学景观。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/nasa-just-found-something-strange-inside-asteroid-bennu-sample.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 11:50:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/nasa-just-found-something-strange-inside-asteroid-bennu-sample</guid></item><item><title>科学家发现如何在视力丧失开始之前阻止它</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-discover-how-to-stop-vision-loss-before-it-starts</link><description>科学家们已经发现了可以保护眼睛视锥细胞免于退化的分子，退化是视力丧失的主要原因。这一发现指出了新的药物靶点，甚至发现了可能有害的化合物。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-discover-how-to-stop-vision-loss-before-it-starts.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 11:35:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-discover-how-to-stop-vision-loss-before-it-starts</guid></item><item><title>地中海并不安全：科学家警告海啸不可避免</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-mediterranean-isnt-safe-scientists-warn-of-inevitable-tsunami</link><description>与普遍看法相反，地中海存在严重且未被充分认识的海啸风险，海浪能够在几分钟内袭击海岸线。地中海经常被视为海啸低风险区，但这一假设正日益受到挑战。历史记录&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-mediterranean-isnt-safe-scientists-warn-of-inevitable-tsunami.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 11:20:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-mediterranean-isnt-safe-scientists-warn-of-inevitable-tsunami</guid></item><item><title>变暖的水域正在加剧阿拉斯加的入侵捕食者</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/warming-waters-are-supercharging-an-invasive-predator-in-alaska</link><description>河流温度升高导致入侵的白斑狗鱼吃掉更多的鱼，威胁到已经减少的鲑鱼数量。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/warming-waters-are-supercharging-an-invasive-predator-in-alaska.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 11:05:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/warming-waters-are-supercharging-an-invasive-predator-in-alaska</guid></item><item><title>研究人员发现南极海域隐藏的基因世界</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/researchers-uncover-hidden-genetic-world-beneath-antarctic-seas</link><description>对南极水域进行的全面基因调查揭示了一个隐藏的微生物世界，对地球气候有着难以言喻的影响。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/researchers-uncover-hidden-genetic-world-beneath-antarctic-seas.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 10:50:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/researchers-uncover-hidden-genetic-world-beneath-antarctic-seas</guid></item><item><title>40% 的受欺凌儿童表现出创伤的临床症状</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/40-of-bullied-children-show-clinical-symptoms-of-trauma</link><description>欺凌只是一种“成人仪式”吗？一项新的研究表明，同伴受害会导致 40% 的小学生出现临床创伤症状。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/40-of-bullied-children-show-clinical-symptoms-of-trauma.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 10:35:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/40-of-bullied-children-show-clinical-symptoms-of-trauma</guid></item></channel></rss>